quran[110]{c,v,t}:
  18,1,"Okhwitsomibwa khwoosi nikhwa Nyasaye, oweshia Eshitabu khumusumba wuwe, ne shiyashikhola okhuba mashiama tawe."
  18,2,"Eshikololofu, kho shikanyilisilie Abandu eshinyasio eshilulu shirulanga khuye, ne shihelesie akomwikhoyo balia basuubilanga, abakholanga ebikhole ebilayi, mbu balinyoola omurungo omulayi."
  18,3,"Bekhalemwo tsinyanga tsioosi."
  18,4,"Ne shikanyilisie balia baboola mbu: “Nyasaye ali nende Omwana.”"
  18,5,"Abo babula obumanyi bwosibwosi bwalio, kata baasabwe bosi. Ni likhuwa likhongo muno lirulanga muminwa chiabu. Shibaboolanga halali obubeyi butswa."
  18,6,"Ne onyala okhwiyira ewe omwene khulwa okhubabelelela ngala bali mbu shibasubilanga amakhuwa kano tawe."
  18,7,"Toto efwe khwakhola ebili khushialo bibe ebirone biashio, kho khubateme ni wina mubo webikhole ebilayi muno."
  18,8,"Ne toto nefwe khulikhola bioosi ebo bili hekulu walio okhuba liloba eliumu."
  18,9,"Nohomba oparanga mbu Abandu ba mumbinga nende kalia kahandikwa, mbu biali ebiamakana okhurulana nende ebimanyisio biefu?"
  18,10,"Olwa Abasiani abo belushila mumbinga, mana nibaboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, khuhelesie tsimbabaasi tsirulanga khwiwe ne khukasilie obulunjifu mulikhuwa liefu.”"
  18,11,"Mana nikhusuba amarwi kabu mumbinga omo khumika eminji."
  18,12,"Mana nikhubalamusia khokhumanye mbu kuli hena khumikanda chibili chino okwabala obulayi muno ebise biabamenya."
  18,13,"Efwe khukhukanilanga amakhuwa kabu khubwatoto. Toto abo ni ababuukha, abasuubila Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, mana nikhubametela obulunjifu."
  18,14,"Mana nikhura amaani mumioyo chiabu olwabeema mana nibaboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi ni Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, shikhulalaamakhwo Nyasaye wundi yesiyesi ulali Ye tawe. Toto awo khulaba khuboolele obubii obwaburirira eshichelo."
  18,15,"Abandu befu bano bakhola abanyasaye balali Ye tawe. Shichila shina nibalarerakhwo eshifune shili habulafu? Kho ni omubii shina omukhongo muno okhushila ulia uchishilanga Nyasaye obubeyi?"""
  18,16,"Ne olwa mwali nimubawukhekhwo nende bilia ebiabalaamanga habundu wa Nyasaye. Mana yilushile mumbinga, Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi alabekulila tsimbabaasi tsitsie, ne alabakholela amakhuwa kenyu okhuba amangu."
  18,17,"Ne olola eliuba olwalirulanga, liburira ehale nende imbinga yabu elubeka womukhono omulunji. Ne olwa likwitsanga ehale ninabo namukhono omukaata, nabo nibali mukhombe mukari we imbinga eyo. Ebo ni bilala khubimanyisio bia Nyasaye. Ulia owa Nyasaye alunjisia, oyo niye omulunjifu. Ne owaakosia, oyo shalamuhelesia omwemeresi wokhumulunjishia tawe."
  18,18,"Ne opara mbu bali meso, nabo khane bakonele. Ne khubakalukhaninjia namukhono mulunji nende namukhono mukata. Ne imbwa yabu nilambisiyie ebilenje biayio mubwinjilililo. Obalolanga, wakhakalukhane lwangu okhubelukha, ne toto oburi obunji bwakhakhwitsulemwo shichila bo."
  18,19,"Kho endio nilwakhwabalamusia kho bareebane abeene khubeene. Naboola omubooli mubo mbu: “Mwikhale tsinyanga tsinga?” Nibaboola mbu: “Khwikhale inyanga ndala nohomba ebuleka weyinyanga.” Nibaboola mbu: “Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi amanyile muno ebise bia mwekhala. Kho, rumekho mulala khwinywe nende amamondo kenyu kano khushiiro mana ahenje eshiakhulia shina eshilayi muno abarerere. Ne akhole amakhuwa kano mumachesi, ne alabarumbulakhwo khuyesiyesi tawe."
  18,20,"Shichila bo nibamanya hamuli, balabalasa amachina, nohomba balabakalusia mumilukha chiabu, ne awo shimulibura kata hatiti tawe.”"
  18,21,"Na endio nilwakhwabarumbusia khobanyoole okhumanya mbu indache ya Nyasaye ni yatoto, ne mbu toto inyanga yeyindukho ibula obukanakani tawe, olwa basolananga abeene khubeene shichila likhuwa liabu. Nibaboola mbu: “Yumbashe inzu ekulu wabu. Nyasaye wabu Omulesi yabamanya obulayi muno.” Balia bashila mulikhuwa liabu nibaboola mbu: “Toto efwe khulombakha omusikiti ekulu wabu.”"
  18,22,"(Abandi) balaboolanga mbu: “Bali Abandu bataru, wakhane wabu ni imbwa yabu.” Ne (abandi) balaboolanga mbu: “Bali abandu barano, ne wakhasasaba wabu ni imbwa yabu.” (Babolanga) khu khutemakho butswa okhuboola akabakorerwe. Ne baboolanga mbu, “Bali abandu saba, ne wamunane wabu ni imbwa yabu.” Boola mbu: ‘‘Nyasaye wanje Omulesi ni umanyile muno mbu bali benga. Abulaho ubamanyile halali batiti butswa. Kho, olayingana ekulu wabo tawe halali okhuyingana khwa hekulu hekulu butswa. Ne olareba amakhuwa kabu omundu yesiyesi mubo tawe."
  18,23,"Ne toto olabolakhwo khu liosiliosi tawe mbu: ‘‘Toto nditsa okhukhola elo mutsuli.”"
  18,24,"Halali (ometekho) “Inshallah (Nyasaye nachama).” Ne yitsulila Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niwibilila, ne boola mbu: “Nyasaye wanje Omulesi alaalunjisia injila ili ahambi muno nende obulunjifu okhushila buno.”"
  18,25,"Ne bamenya mumbinga mwabu omo emika tsimia tsitaru, ne nibametakhwo tisa."
  18,26,"Boola mbu: Nyasaye amanyile muno ebise biabekhala. Niye umanyile akefisile akomwikulu nende khushialo. Nookhulola nende okhuwulila okhulayi khuli khurie okhukhwe. Nabo babula omulindi ulali Ye, naye shatsokasinjiakhwo yesiyesi mukhubusia khukhwe tawe."
  18,27,"Ne soma akawafimbulilwa okhurula mushitabu shia Nyasaye wuwo omulesi. Abulaho unyala okhukalukhasia amakhuwa keke tawe. Nawe sholinyoola owawilushila wosiwosi okhumwilukhaye akhaye okhukhunyoola tawe."
  18,28,"Ne wisumilisie halala nende balia balaamanga Nyasaye wabu Omulesi itsuli nende ingoloobe, nibakhabanga obweni bubwe. Ne olababusiamwo tsimoni tsitsio khulwokhwenya ebirone biobulamu bwokhushialo tawe. Ne olalonda tawe khu balia abakhwalekha bakandala emioyo chiabu mana nibalonda obwikombi bwabu, mana amakhuwa kabu nikabura eshichelo."
  18,29,"Ne boola mbu buno ni obulaamba okhurula khu Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi. Kho, ulia wenya, asuubile, ne owenya, akhaye. Toto efwe khwarecheshela ababii omulilo okwa olukaka lwakwo lulibaterera. Ne nibenya obukhonyi, balikhonywa khumatsi kali shinga amafura kasalulusibwe akalisaamba obweni bwabu. Neeshinywebwa eshibi muno shili shirie shino! Ne ni habundu ali abii muno arie hano!"
  18,30,"Toto balia abasuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, efwe toto shikhukosinjia omurungo kwabalia bakholanga amalayi tawe."
  18,31,"Abo balinyoola emikunda chilaliwa tawe, echiburangamwo emialo, balironwamwo nende ebifwalo biokhumakhono, ebia idhahabu, ne balifwalwa tsingubo tsia obukondo bwobunyasi etsia hariri inyangu nende hariri isiro. Balikhalamwo khubitali ebiaronwa (khufono). Ni omurungo omulayi kuli kuriena kuno! Ne ni habundu alayi ali arie hano!"
  18,32,"Ne bachelasilie abasatsa babili, mulala wabu khwamukholela emikunda chibili chetsizabibu, mana nikhuchibotokhanilia mitende, ne hakari wachio nikhuraho emisala chindi chieyimele."
  18,33,"Emikunda chibili chino chioosi chietsulamwo ebiamo biachio, ne shikhwachilemiakhwo shiosishiosi tawe. Ne mukari mwachio nikhubusiamwo omwalo."
  18,34,"Ne yali nende ebiamo ebinji. Mana naboolela owashie nibakalusaninjia mbu: “Esie ekhushila khumwandu nende amaani khulwa Abandu bendi ninabo.”"
  18,35,"Mana niyenjila mumukunda kukwe niyekholele obubii, naboola mbu: “Shembara omukunda kuno nikulibiyakhwo tawe, tsinyanga tsioosi."
  18,36,"Ne shembara indukho nilibaho tawe. Ne kata nibiba mbu engalusibwa wa Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, toto ndilinyoola wokhukalukhawo andayi muno okhushila kano.”"
  18,37,"Owashie namuboolela nibakalusaninjia mbu: “Koo, okhayanga ulia wakhuloonga khuliloba, mana khu indonyande ya amatsi kolwibulo, mana nakhukhola omundu omulaamba?”"
  18,38,"Owashie namuboolela nibakalusaninjia mbu: “Koo, okhayanga ulia wakhuloonga khuliloba, mana khu indonyande ya amatsi kolwibulo, mana nakhukhola omundu omulaamba?”"
  18,39,"Mana olaboolangakhwo lwawenjira mumukunda kukwo mbu: “Biendi nabo bino Nyasaye niye wanyenyera, amaani shikanyolekhanga halali khu Nyasaye. Ni undolanga mbu endi nende omwandu omutiti nende abana batiti okhushila ewe."
  18,40,"Awundi Nyasaye wanje Omulesi alambelesia eshilayi okhushila omukunda kukwo, ne arumile omukunda oko likulu okhurula mwikulu mana kube liloba likhaya lirerekhanga."
  18,41,"Nohomba amatsi kakwo kakhame obule okhukanyoola.”"
  18,42,"Mana ebiamo biaye nibibotokhanwa, mana natong’a okhukalukhania amakhono keke, khulwa obukhalabani bwaye omo nabio (ebiamo) nibibula khumisala chabyo, mana naboola mbu: “Ehh! Emanyangakhwo, shindakhatsokasiye Nyasaye wanje Omulesi nende shiosishiosi tawe.”"
  18,43,"Kho, shiyali nende omukanda kwokhumukhonya tawe ehale nende Nyasaye, naye omwene shiyali unyala okhwikhonya tawe."
  18,44,"Eyo obulindi bwatoto nibwa Nyasaye butswa owatoto. Ye niye omurunji omulayi muno, owokhurera obumalilishi obulayi."
  18,45,"Ne bachelasilie obulamu bwokhushialo mbu buli shinga amatsi kakhwishinjia okhurula mwikulu, mana nikesaasia nende emimela chiomwiloba, mana emimela echo nichiba amasafu amomu, akakhalishe khalishe akomuyaka kuwutsanga eyi nende eyi. Ne Nyasaye ali nende obunyali muno khubuli eshindu."
  18,46,"Omwandu nende Abana ni ebirone biobulamu bwokhushialo. Ne ebikhole ebilayi bitong’anga nibo obulayi imbeli wa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khumurungo nende okhusuubilila okhulayi."
  18,47,"Ne inyanga yakhulichesia efikulu, ne olilola eshialo nishili eshiang’ang’u, ne khulibalamusia ne shikhulilekha yesiyesi mubo tawe."
  18,48,"Ne baliemibwa imbeli wa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olunyaali. Toto enywe mukhwitsile shingala khwabalonga olwambeli. Halali mwaparanga mbu shikhulibarereraho ebise bino tawe."
  18,49,"Ne Eshitabu shilirebwaho imbeli (wabu). Kho, olilola shinga ababii baliria muno shichila kalia kalimwo. Ne baliboola mbu: “Oh bayie, Eshitabu shino shibere shirie, sishilesherekho lititi nohomba likhongo tawe halali shialihandika obulayi muno.” Ne balinyoola koosi kabakhola nikali hawo. Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi shakholelanga yesiyesi obubii tawe."
  18,50,"Ne olwakhwaboolela abamalaika mbu: “Rerere Adam obweni hasi.” Mana nibara obweni hasi halali Ibilis, ye yali okhurula mumajini, mana nafunaka lilako lia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi. Koo, mumukholanga ye nende olwibulo lulwe abalina (benyu) habundu wa Nyasaye, nabo nabasuku benyu? Ni obubii buli burie buno bwababii bakalukhaninjia."
  18,51,"Shindabakhola okhuba abaloli bookhulongwa khwelikulu nende eshialo nohomba okhulongwa khwabu abeene tawe. Ne shindakhola abakosinjia okhuba abakhonyi tawe."
  18,52,"Ne inyanga yaliboola mbu: “Rerekhwo abamwasanjinjia ninaasi abamwachikhanga” mana balibalanga, halali shibalibafuchililila tawe, mana khulira hakari wabu eshikalilo."
  18,53,"Ne Ababii balilola omulilo, ne balimanya mbu okhula balenjilamwo, ne mana shibalinyoola amelushilo tawe."
  18,54,"Ne toto khwaboolela Abandu Mukurani ino buli imbia yokhufwanania. Halali Omundu yabura eshichelo okhushila buli eshindu mukhuyingana."
  18,55,"Ne shibulaho shiekayila Abandu okhusuubila olwa obulunjifu bwabetsela mana basabe eshileshelo khu Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, halali kaboolele kalia akabakhale, nohomba eshinyasio shibetsele nibalolanga."
  18,56,"Ne shikhurumanga Abarumwa tawe halali babe bokhuhana akomwikhoyo nende abokhwikanyilisia. Ne balia bakhaya bayingananga khu kobubeyi mbu khubakwisie hasi obwatoto khuko. Ne bakholanga tsinyali tsianje nende kalia akabekanyilisibwa okhuba omubayo."
  18,57,"Ne ni wina omubii omukhongo okhushila ulia owitsulisibungwa tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi mana atsileche mana niyebilila akemikhono chichie chiaranjilisia. Toto efwe khwara efisubo khumioyo chiabu kho bakhaye okhuchimanya obulayi, ne khwara mumarwi kabu shiokhukeekasia. Ne nobalanga khubulunjifu, shibakhachama okhulunjikha tawe."
  18,58,"Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye Omunji weshileshelo, Owetsimbabaasi. Alababukulilanga obubii khulwa kalia akabakhola, toto yakhabarerere eshinyasio lwangu lwangu. Halali bali nende ebise ebia balalinyoola amelushilo kosikosi akokhumwilukha tawe."
  18,59,"Ne etso ni tsingongo etsia khwatsisishia olwa tsiakhola obubii, nikhubarererao ebise biokhusikha khwabu."
  18,60,"Ne olwa Musa yaboolela omusiani waye mbu: “Ndalatsililila okhutsia, okhula ndule wetsinyanza tsibili tsibukanilanga nohomba enzililile okhutsia emika nemika.”"
  18,61,"Kho olwa boola we tsinyanza etso tsibukanilanga, nibebilila inyeni yabu, mana nayo nitsililila okhutsia imbeli munyanza."
  18,62,"Olwa babura mana niboola imbeli, yaboolela omusiani wuwe oyo mbu: “Khwelesie eshiakhulia shiefu shieshitere. Toto khunyoolele khuluchendo lwefu luno amachonye.”"
  18,63,"Naboola mbu: “Olutsi, wakhuwulushile halia khushitulo? Esie toto ndibilile inyeni eyo. Ne abulaho owakhola ndebilila halali Shetani mbu ndalayitsulila tawe, mana niitila injila yayo niitsia munyanza okhutsia khwamakana."""
  18,64,"Naboola mbu: “Awo niho wakhwenyerenje.” Mana nibakalukha inyuma okhulonda injila yabu ilia ilia."
  18,65,"Mana nibanyoola Omusumba mubasumba befu owakhwahelesia tsimbabaasi okhurula khwifwe, ne owakhwechesia amasomo okhurula khwifwe."
  18,66,"Musa namuboolela mbu: “Koo, enyala ndakhulondakhwo unzechesiekhwo kobulunjifu kawechesibwa?”"
  18,67,"Naboola mbu: “Toto ewe shonyala okhwifwila okhuba halala ninasi tawe."
  18,68,"Ne onyala orie okhwifwila kalia akolakamanyile obulayi muno tawe?”"
  18,69,"Naboola mbu: “Nyasaye nachama, witsa okhuunyoola nendi omwisumilisi, ne shinditsa okhulobakhwo likhuwa lilio liosiliosi tawe.”"
  18,70,"Naboola mbu: “Mana niwunondakhwo, olandeeba liosiliosi tawe okhula esie anjake okhukhuboolela hekulu walio.”"
  18,71,"Mana nibarula, ne olwa banina mubwaro, nabufutula. Musa namureeba mbu: ‘‘Ofutule obwaro kho osishie abalimwo? Toto okholele likhuwa libii muno.”"
  18,72,"Naboola mbu: “Shekhuboolelekhwo mbu sholanyala okwifwila ninasi tawe?”"
  18,73,"Naboola mbu: “Olambukulila obubii khukandibilile tawe, ne olasitoyelia amakhuwa kanje tawe.”"
  18,74,"Mana boosi nibarula halala, nibanyoola Omusiani mulala mana namwira. Musa naboola mbu: “Ahh! Wirire omundu eshikhaya ubula libii, ulerere Omundu tawe? Toto okholele likhuwa libii muno.”"
  18,75,"Naboola mbu: “Koo, shekhuboolelekhwo mbu sholanyala okhwifwila halala ninasi tawe?”"
  18,76,"Naboola mbu: “Nekhureeba liosiliosi khandi, olaandekha okhuba halala ninawe khandi tawe. Shichila omalile okhunyoola eshifune okhurula khwisie.”"
  18,77,"Mana nibatsililila okhutsia, okhula olwa boolela Abandu bolukongo lulala, nibareeba abeene olukongo olo eshiakhulia, nibaloba okhubeyamira obucheni, ne nibanyoolamwo (mulukongo olo) lisisi nilienyanga okhukwa, mana naliemia. Musa naboola mbu: “Noli uchama, wakhabukule omurungo khulwa elo.”"
  18,78,"Naboola mbu: “Hano ni wakhulekhanira esie ninawe. Nditsa okhukhuboolela obwatoto bwakalia kolanyalile okhwisumilisia khuko tawe."
  18,79,"Kho eliaro lilia liali lia abamanani bakholanga munyanza, ne nindenya mbu elirekhwo isoni, shichila imbeli wabu Omwami yaliyo ubukulanga buli eliaro lilayi khumaani."
  18,80,"Ne omusiani ulia, abebusi bebe bali abasuubili, nikhuria mbu aletsa yabayila mubukori bwokhubura eshichero nende okhukhaya."
  18,81,"Kho mana khwenya mbu Nyasaye wabu Omulesi abakalukhasirie omwana omulayi okhushila oyo, khubutswenufu, nende owuli ahambi muno khushisa."
  18,82,"Nalo lisisi lilia, liali lia abaana abafwilwa babili, mulitokho elo, ne hasi walio kwaliho omwandu kwabu, ne samwana yali omundu omulayi, kho Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yenya mbu bakubuye mana berusilie abeene omwandu kwabu oko, etso nitsimbabaasi tsirula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi. Ne shekholele kano khubunyali bwanje tawe. Obo nibo obwatoto bwa kalia akokhayilwe okhwifwila khuko."""
  18,83,"Ne bakhurebanga amakhuwa ka Dhul’karnain, boola mbu: “Nditsa okhubasomela amakhuwa keke kandi.”"
  18,84,"Toto efwe khwamura obulai muno khushialo, ne nikhumuwa injila yokhunyoola buli eshindu."
  18,85,"Mana naloonda injila."
  18,86,"Okhuula shingala yoola ebukwe weliuba, yalinyola liheranga khusebere eya amatoyi amanji. Awo nanyoola Abandu. Nikhuboola mbu: “Ewe Dhul’karnain, bahelesie eshinyasio nohomba obakholele obulayi.”"
  18,87,"Naboola mbu: “Ulia owakhola obubii, khwitsa okhumuwa eshinyasio, mana alikalusibwa khu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, naye alimuhelesia eshinyasio eshibii muno."
  18,88,"Ne ulia owasuubila mana nakhola ebikhole ebilayi, alanyoola omurungo omulayi, nafu khwitsa okhumuboolela amakhuwa kefu amangu."
  18,89,"Mana naloonda injila."
  18,90,"Okhula shingala yoola weliuba lirulilanga (mumbo), yalinyola nilirulilanga khubandu abalakhwarereraho eshishinjilo shiokhubekalila okhurulana ninalio tawe."
  18,91,"Ne shinga endio khwali nikhumanyile obulayi amakhuwa koosi kayali ninako."
  18,92,"Mana naloonda injila."
  18,93,"Okhula shingala yoola hakari wetsingulu tsibili, yanyoola inyuma watsio abandu balawulilanga amakhuwa tawe."
  18,94,"Nibaboola mbu: “Ewe Dhul-Karnain, toto Yaajuj nende Maajuj, bakholanga obuononi khushyalo. Kho khukhwelesie omurungo ore eshikalilo hakari wefu ninabo?”"
  18,95,"Naboola mbu: “Kalia ka Nyasaye wanje Omulesi yandinyisiliamwo ni amalayi muno. Kho, mukhoonye nende amaani, ndalara hakari wenyu ninabo eshikalilo eshisiro."
  18,96,"Munderere ebitonye bieshichuma.” okhula shingala yetsusia obwiyangu buli hakari wetsingulu tsibili etso, naboola mbu: ‘‘Bwaane (omulilo)” okhula shingala yakhola eshichuma esho omulilo, naboola mbu: ‘‘Nderere ishaba isalulushe enzushe khuno.”"
  18,97,"Mana shibanyala okhushinina bashiambuka, nohomba okhuyabamo obwina tawe."
  18,98,"Naboola mbu: “Tsino ni tsimbabaasi okhurula khu Nyasaye wanje Omulesi. Ne olwa yiliula indache ya Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, alishifunakafunaka muno. Ne indache ya Nyasaye wanje Omulesi ni yahabwene."""
  18,99,"Ne khulibalekha abeene khubeene beenjiranemwo, ne olwa olwika lulifurwamwo, awo khulibakhung’asia boosi halala."
  18,100,"Ne khulilolosia Jahanamu inyanga eyo imbeli wabakhayi malolosia."
  18,101,"Abetsimoni tsiabu tsiali tsiafunikhwa ehale nende ametsulilo kefu, ne shibali nibanyala okhuwulila tawe."
  18,102,"Koo, balia abakhaya baparanga mbu banyala okhukhola Abasumba banje abalina babu habundu wanje? Toto efwe khwarecheshela Jahannam abakhayi ibe wabaliishila."
  18,103,"Boola mbu: “Koo, ebabilekhwo balia bebikhole biabu biabiiya muno?”"
  18,104,"Ni balia bobukhalabani bwabu bwakora eshikhaya mubulamu bwokhushialo, nabo baparanga mbu bakholanga ebikhole ebilayi."
  18,105,"Abo nibo bakhaya ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi nende okhubukana ninaye. Kho, ebikhole biabu nibikwa akhaya, ne shikhulibateba inyanga yeyindukho tawe."
  18,106,"Kho, Jahanam nikwo omurungo kwabu shichila bakhaya mana nibakholela omubayo ebimanyisio bianje nende Abarumwa banje."
  18,107,"Toto balia abasuubila mana nibakhola amalayi, ameshelo kabu kaliba Firdaws."
  18,108,"Balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi, shibalienya okhurulamwo tawe."
  18,109,"Boola mbu: “Inyanza yibetsanga mbu nibwo obwino bwokhuhandika amakhuwa ka Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, inyanza yakhomele amakhuwa ka Nyasaye wanje Omulesi nikashili okhuwa, kata khureranga etsindi shinga etso."
  18,110,"Boola mbu: “Toto esie endisa Omundu shinga enywe, efimbulilungwa mbu Nyasaye wenyu ni Nyasaye mulala. Kho, ulia wikomba okhubukana nende Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi, akhole ebikhole ebilayi, ne alatsokaasiakhwo yesiyesi khumalamo ka Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi tawe."""
